channel.title: SkyNet || Going to Terminate Every Other RSPS || 317 || Delta ||
channel.description:
[center][size=6][font=impact]I'LL BE BUSY WITH SCHOOL FOR A LITTLE BIT SEEING AS I HAVE MULTIPLE PROJECTS AND TESTS COMING UP. I'LL TRY TO RESUME DEVELOPMENT ASAP.[/font][/size] [center][img]http://i40.tinypic.com/wak8y8.jpg[/img][/center]
[hr] [font=georgia][b][i]Skynet: The RSPS no one can shut down but John Connor[/i][/b][/font] [hr]
[hr] [font=andale mono][i][b]My Goals For This Server[/b][/i][/font] [/center] [hr]
[hr] Green = Completed Yellow = Started Red = Incomplete
[hr] [size=4] [b]-Overall-[/b][/size]
[ul][li]-Fully add a PVP system along with Perfect combat[/li] [li]-Create Fully new map locations never used before[/li] [li]-New shops, with new shop owners (who is sick of all the same shops?)[/li] [li]-Create Custom mini games (i'm second guessing this one. Might take a while)[/li] [li]-Create a good XP Rate (not too much, and not too little)[/li] [li]-Make it so your able to follow people with clipping.[/li] [li]-NPC clipping[/li] [li]-Make a good environment, that makes people want to play the server.[/li] [li]-Random Events :) [/li] [li]-Make a good NPC auto spawn.[/li] [li]-Combat (Including Made and Range) :[/li] [li]-Create a good PVP system[/li] [li]-Aggressive and non aggressive NPCs [/li] [li]-EVERY item has a required level (RS based)[/li] [li]-EVERY item is equipped to the right spot.[/li] [li]-Specs are correct.[/li] [li]-Stats are correct.[/li] [li]-Constant/ non Constant attacking.[/li] [li]-100% working potions[/li] [li]-Every weapon does what its supposed to do[/li] [li]-gfx are correct.[/li] [li]-wield emotes are correct.[/li] [li]-Mage runes deplete.[/li] [li]-Able to pickup 90% of shot arrows.[/li][/ul]
[b][i]-Agility -Have at least 2 courses working. -Have a use. Not just leveling up for no reason -Create a custom course (I haven't decided yet)
[b][i][i][b]-Cooking: -Can cook every Meat on the game -Working extras such as cakes and drinks -Able to cook on fires, as well as ranges. -Food gets burnt, depending on the player's level, and what is being cooked. -Food heals HP.
[i][i][b]-Crafting: -Working leathers -Gems can be crushed (Much like burning in cooking) -Able to make money from this skill -Enchant gems for amulets and rings
-[b][i][i][b]Farming: -Make every seed work -Make every (or most) patches work -Just like RS
[b][i][i][b]Firemaking: -All logs can burn. -Clipping after burning (so people cant do the 'Firemaking Noclip' Glitch) -Turn to ashes after a set time -Make 'Attempts' depending on the player's level -Can light candles, etc.
[b][i][i][b]Fishing: -Working spots all around the map with different fish -Catch rate depends on player's Level -All types of fishing working.
[b][i][i][b]Fletching: -EVERY type of logs can be fletched -Every log has an option to be a long bow or short bow -Working arrow making with different tips -Able to string bows -Able to Make cross bows.
[b][i][i][b]Herblore: -Make every potion with correct ingredients -Not every ingredient is sold in a shop -Working bonuses.
[b][i][i][b]Mining: -Every rock working -Real locations along with new ones -Possibility to get a gem. -Must have pick ax equipped to mine. -Possibility to have your pick ax lose its head. -Correct re-spawn time. -Correct 'Attempts' based on plater's level.
[b][i][i][b]Prayer: -All bones working with different XP -All prayers working correctly -Can use bones on alter for 3x XP
[b][i][i][b]Runecrafting: -Correct alter positions fully working -Real alters along with the Abyss(?) -Number of runes you get is based upon player's level -Working with Rune ess and Pure ess
[b][i][i][b]Slayer: -Lots of tasks: Noob, Easy, Med, Hard, Insane -Slayer tower with all monsters -Slayer monsters around the whole map -Slayer Rewards.
[b][i][i][b]Thieving: -ALL stalls working -Money/item stealing depending on stall -Wait time, along with Randoms -Able to steal from NPCs -Level depends on how fast you can steal
[b][i][i][b]Woodcutting: -All trees on map able to be cut. -Create a log gain rate -Random: ax gets bent or falls off (don't remember which one was WC) -All axes can cut the trees -Ax must be equipped to cut the trees
[hr] [size=4][b][i]UPDATES:[/i][/b] [/size][code] Started Work On Server
[/code]
[hr] [center][b][i]Pictures:[/i][/b]
[b][i]Will Add As Soon As More Things Are Done [/i][/b] [hr]
[hr] [size=4]Supporters: -g0d of war1 -Runescape Sucks -Tinyscape -Kronixz -Neroxx -Kenno [/size] [hr]
[hr] [size=4]Credits:
Daginith (Me) RandQm (For Base) <3 [/size] [hr]
[/center]
